    • Method Detail

      • getFeed

        TStream<T> getFeed()
        Get the stream feeding this sink. The returned reference may be used for further processing of the feeder stream.
        For example, s.print().filter(...)
        Here the filter is applied to s so that s feeds the print() and filter().
        Returns:
        stream feeding this sink.
